Show balance, solidify pitch furniture, restore mowed stripes, beef up canopy

- HUD: stop ignoring the top inset so the coin/gem balance bar renders BELOW
  Roblox's menu strip instead of hidden under it (you could only see income).
- Pitch: high-contrast mowed stripes lifted above the now-rendering grass
  texture so it reads as a striped pitch again, not flat turf.
- Hoardings (advertising boards) and goal posts are now solid (CanCollide) —
  no more walking through them.
- Perimeter wall canopy: thicker (2.5), raised on taller 10-stud walls, larger
  inward cantilever, and solid — a real stadium roof lip instead of a thin sheet.

